OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773162681
OL,3,CUK warship HMS Dragon sets sail for
OL,4,CCyprus amid Middle East crisis
OL,6,FThe UK warship, HMS Dragon, has set
OL,7,Fsail from Portsmouth Naval Base for
OL,8,Fthe Eastern Mediterranean, as the
OL,9,Fconflict in the Middle East continues.
OL,11,FThe Royal Navy destroyer, which has
OL,12,Fbeen loaded with ammunition, will be
OL,13,Fused to protect British base, RAF
OL,14,FAkrotiri in Cyprus, after it was hit
OL,15,Fby a drone.
OL,17,FThe 200-strong crew can be seen
OL,18,Fstanding onboard the Type-45 Destroyer
OL,19,Fas the ship passes the naval base.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
