OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773162681
OL,3,CUK warship HMS Dragon sets sail for
OL,4,CCyprus amid Middle East crisis
OL,6,FAround 100 people could be seen waving
OL,7,Fthe ship and her crew off from the
OL,8,Fdock.
OL,10,FOne woman who spoke to ITV News said
OL,11,Fher youngest son is onboard HMS Dragon
OL,12,Fafter joining the Royal Navy two and a
OL,13,Fhalf years ago.
OL,15,F"He was assigned Dragon as his main
OL,16,Fship, so we've just found out they're
OL,17,Foff so I wanted to be here today. I'm
OL,18,Freally excited for him and he's
OL,19,Fexcited.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773162681
OL,3,CUK warship HMS Dragon sets sail for
OL,4,CCyprus amid Middle East crisis
OL,6,F"He's nervous as it's such an unknown
OL,7,Fsituation, but he's done the training
OL,8,Fand it seems like the best kind of
OL,9,Fship we've got."
OL,11,FThe war began with joint US-Israeli
OL,12,Fattacks on Iran on February 28 and has
OL,13,Fsince escalated to the wider region,
OL,14,Fwith Iran striking its Gulf neighbours
OL,15,Fand Israel launching an offensive in
OL,16,Fsouthern Lebanon and Beirut.
OL,18,FThe US Secretary of Defence Pete
OL,19,FHegseth said Tuesday will be the "most
OL,20,Fintense" attack on Iran yet as the
OL,21,Fconflict entered its 11th day.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
