OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773162682
OL,3,CUK warship HMS Dragon sets sail for
OL,4,CCyprus amid Middle East crisis
OL,6,FYesterday (Monday), the Prime Minister
OL,7,FKeir Starmer said the war could hit
OL,8,F"every household and every business"
OL,9,Fin the UK, as he promised "to get
OL,10,Fahead" of any potential impact on
OL,11,Fpeople's finances.
OL,13,FThe Government has come under fire for
OL,14,Fthe time it has taken to get HMS
OL,15,FDragon ready for deployment, with The
OL,16,FRoyal Navy confirming at the weekend
OL,17,Fthat she would depart some time this
OL,18,Fweek.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
