OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773162682
OL,3,CUK warship HMS Dragon sets sail for
OL,4,CCyprus amid Middle East crisis
OL,6,FAsked by journalists why there was no
OL,7,FType 45 destroyer sent to the region
OL,8,Fmonths ago during a US military build-
OL,9,Fup, officials said increasingly
OL,10,Ffragile geopolitics with many
OL,11,Fdifferent security threats made the
OL,12,Fsituation complex.
OL,14,FHMS Dragon was chosen because it was
OL,15,Fthe readiest for the mission,
OL,16,Fofficials said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
