OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773162682
OL,3,CUK warship HMS Dragon sets sail for
OL,4,CCyprus amid Middle East crisis
OL,6,FAccording to the Royal Navy, the
OL,7,Fship's main role is air defence, and
OL,8,Fproviding protection to her fellow
OL,9,Fships by detecting, interrogating and
OL,10,Fneutralising enemy threats with the
OL,11,Ffearsome Sea Viper anti-air missile
OL,12,Fsystem.
OL,14,FThe destroyer's voyage from Portsmouth
OL,15,Fto Cyprus is expected to take several
OL,16,Fdays.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
