OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773162682
OL,3,CUK warship HMS Dragon sets sail for
OL,4,CCyprus amid Middle East crisis
OL,6,FLast year Dragon herself became the
OL,7,Ffirst British warship to destroy a
OL,8,Fmissile travelling at supersonic speed
OL,9,Fduring an international exercise off
OL,10,FScotland, obliterating the target
OL,11,Fdespite its attempts to corkscrew and
OL,12,Fweave to avoid Sea Viper.
OL,14,FFleet Commander Vice-Admiral Steve
OL,15,FMoorhouse said: "I am proud that our
OL,16,Fhighly-professional personnel have
OL,17,Fresponded in a short time to ensure
OL,18,FHMS Dragon and the Wildcats from 815
OL,19,FNaval Air Squadron are fully prepared
OL,20,Ffor their mission."
OL,26,@wD@QOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
