OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1773162682
OL,3,CUK warship HMS Dragon sets sail for
OL,4,CCyprus amid Middle East crisis
OL,6,FHMS Dragon's Commanding Officer,
OL,7,FCommander Iain Giffin, said: "My
OL,8,Fship's company have worked tirelessly
OL,9,Fto ensure we are ready for our mission
OL,10,Fto the Eastern Mediterranean.
OL,12,F"I am proud of professional manner in
OL,13,Fwhich they have responded.
OL,15,F"We are trained for this, we are ready
OL,16,Ffor this, we have the equipment and
OL,17,Fpeople, we have the support of the
OL,18,FBritish people and, most importantly,
OL,19,Four families and friends."
OL,26,@oD@^OUtD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
